{"tid":1800703,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"28~29 上水和你shop重點留意事項","createTime":"2019-12-28T05:34:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-28T06:12:53.000Z","uid":329059,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"87582ff39057bd370952dd1802575d8b3f1746a8","tid":1800703,"uid":329059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T05:34:30.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">上水和你shop重點留意事項</span></span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n0. 必須熟讀地圖，唔識路請搵熟路手足帶路。本區熟路手足盡可能協助外區手足逃生／離場。<br />\n1. 便衣狗並唔會單獨行動，附近必定有同伴。<br />\n2. 有便衣狗的話，附近一定有一隊防暴standby，救人時間大概只有30秒。<br />\n3. 切勿穿著容易辨認嘅衣物，例如紅色衫，有LOGO嘅衫。<br />\n4. 預早計劃逃生路線，亦需要計劃後備逃生路線。<br />\n5. 預留逃生位置，亦即係企疏啲。<br />\n6. 留意狗隻部署，如果發現商場／手足位置已經被包圍，代表狗隻即將清場，逃生時間約只有2分鐘。<br />\n7. 要屌狗唔該企前面，企後面屌狗會害死前面嘅手足。<br />\n8. 食花生／屌狗，請預留緩衝距離(最少10米)。<br />\n9. 打狗屌狗唔係主要目標，商場／鋪頭做唔成生意已經達成目標，切勿戀戰死守。<br />\n10. 目標達成請轉場，勿死守空城。<br />\n11. 上水天橋四通八達，請好好利用。<br />\n12. 小心回馬槍。<br />\n<br />\n邊度重狗就唔去邊度，be water.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">【哨】北區驗證資訊站 :</span> <a href=\"https://t.me/northstation\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fnorthstation&d=CRZj9ITMXIzKHLmvffUzPAogPkW5zMkxdNnzPoGklno%3D&h=4f9888c5\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/northstation</a>"},{"pid":"d8148db723eba1488b0564063d1553097619940a","tid":1800703,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T05:39:26.000Z","msg":"（聯署）你班友快Ｄ同我簽晒佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1799015\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1799015</a>"},{"pid":"dc9dbbb8fcef6b69a97035260eb4532a0713b26c","tid":1800703,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T05:40:45.000Z","msg":"上水好多商場, 仲要連住, 好方便<br />\n唔好死守"},{"pid":"bc97467d55de2433f8869f007292fd281ef6cf60","tid":1800703,"uid":49018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T06:08:12.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"832dac8dfc2e91889c3de3575bc2b133469ed8eb","tid":1800703,"uid":49018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T06:08:27.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"b89302ba55fc0e13b11a91c68396c0126d744fbf","tid":1800703,"uid":157037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T06:09:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6579f7531033ee874f97d130ae81d10356c71896","tid":1800703,"uid":325840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T06:09:46.000Z","msg":"好驚俾狗咬而慢慢變返港豬嘅唔該入一入嚟<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1800681\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1800681</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"db54510325d4278cedc87c64256e7af31f0a2049","tid":1800703,"uid":265917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T06:12:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">想多啲人參與行動？</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">要記住嚟場革命唔係淨係屬於後生仔<br />\n四五十歲既人多數淨係上fb 佢地好多時都想參與行動 但又唔知有咩日程</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>我地有咩可以做？</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>1）我地要多啲<span style=\"color: red;\">係fb唔同post下面瘋狂洗版行動文宣</span><br />\n2）仲有要<span style=\"color: red;\">係街不斷airdrop啲文宣</span>俾人製造抗爭氣氛<br />\n3）隨身袋住啲文宣周街貼</strong></span><br />\n <br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>唔好淨係依賴文宣組<br />\n頭兩項都係零成本 <br />\n你唔係唔做呀嘛</strong></span></span>"}]}